title: 116 Music videos by Ayumi Hamasaki With English Subtitles
description:
116 Music videos by Ayumi Hamasaki With English Subtitles in 720p updated

Mediainfo:
Video #0          : AVC at 5 000 Kbps / 5 000 Kbps
Aspect            : 1280 x 720 (1.778) at 30.000 fps
Audio #0          : AAC at 320 Kbps
Infos             : 2 channels, 44.1 KHz

All videos have as video source blu-ray, except for "Shake it", "NaNaNa", "Return Road", "how beautiful you are", "Feel the love" and "Merry-go-round" that are upscaled from DVD.
All videos have as audio source the FLAC album version.
Subtiles are harcoded. English translations by masa and Misa-chan.
Some videos have been reedited to match the original version of the song.
